{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b412461c90","title":"社会学工作筹备委员会第一次会议","origin":"《反对资产阶级社会科学复辟(第三辑)》，北京：科学出版社，1958年3月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"77a0f44962","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":9,"articleId":"b412461c90"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"004954eec0","name":"吴景超"},{"id":"94a10490d0","name":"吴文藻"},{"id":"99d58605a9","name":"李景汉"},{"id":"b69c13ddae","name":"费孝通"},{"id":"bbb82ce4e0","name":"陈达"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8cffa85744","type":"title","text":"社会学工作筹备委员会第一次会议","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"cc4f220a4d","type":"authors","text":"费孝通吴景超李景汉吴文藻陈达","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"03bf4bfe27","type":"subtitle","text":"社会学工作筹备委员会第一次会议","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"9c15d8d4c3","type":"paragraph","text":"出席人：费孝通、雷洁琼、吴景超、李景汉、吴文藻、陈达、袁方","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"0feaf1bc95","type":"paragraph","text":"时间：1957年6月9日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"bcd88649de","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：南太常寺甲12号","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"62d57ba713","type":"paragraph","text":"主持人：陈达","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"8012eb6069","type":"paragraph","text":"记录：袁方","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"71b822c508","type":"subtitle","text":"(一)陈达报告本会成立以来的情况，以及今后如何开展工作。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"c2b95b8a20","type":"paragraph","text":"1．本会成立以来，收到不少来信，这些信件的内容可以分为以下几类：","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"9d6ff09de0","type":"paragraph","text":"一、祝贺","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"237e3c97dd","type":"paragraph","text":"二、询问工作如何开展","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"c81792810c","type":"paragraph","text":"三、找工作","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"55dc08740b","type":"paragraph","text":"2．今后如何开展","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"d4a5269fd6","type":"paragraph","text":"科学院今年在经费和编制上虽有困难，但为了本会工作的开展仍准备了一些经费(约5万元)及编制名额(5人左右)。我们应本勤俭办科学的精神，重点开展工作，但应全面考虑社会学方面的安排，有步骤的来进行。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"f9a5da0f72","type":"paragraph","text":"雷洁琼报告上海社会学界同人最近活动情况，多数人都主张在复旦大学恢复社会学系。他们已经开了一个会，组织起来，先做一些调查研究工作。今后本会应与他们取得联系。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"61c0c7a971","type":"paragraph","text":"3．讨论事项：","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"6d292fec9f","type":"paragraph","text":"关于本会名称和任务：","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"50b5095903","type":"paragraph","text":"名称：社会学工作委员会，隶属科学院哲学社会科学部。推陈达担任主任委员。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"00ad7130ff","type":"paragraph","text":"任务：","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"cfefc34f59","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)团结与联系原来社会学界同人，筹备成立中国社会学会；研究机构。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"92207f4f54","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)讨论和建议有关社会调查研究工作的方案。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"5141744be3","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)筹备成立社会学的研究机构和社会学系。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"b96fa7b021","type":"subtitle","text":"（二）关于社会调查研究工作：","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"39ff676eef","type":"paragraph","text":"北京社会学界同人的调查研究工作暂分人口、劳动、城乡社区调查与民族等方面进行。其它地方(上海等)可由该地同人结合当地具体情况开展工作。北京方面的调查研究工作如下：","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"461bada293","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、人口与劳动调查研究(附农村调查)拟暂由劳动干校负责，与科学院合作。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"ae5df32c3d","type":"paragraph","text":"一、建议科学院成立社会调查研究所。直属哲学社会科学部。但根据目前条件先成立人口学研究室。由哲学社会科学部领导。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"4a00385b71","type":"appellation","text":"二、(原稿不清楚)","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"39a073cad5","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)人口理论组。研究项目：马克思列宁主义人口理论；新中国1953年全国人口普查以及对于今后人口普查的具体办法与建议；国际人口(苏联，人民民主国家及资本主义国家的人口)；中国历史上的人口等。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"0bd4c72ae1","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)人事登记组。研究项目：人事登记制度；地区人口(城市，乡村，少数民族地区)；移民(国际与国内移民问题)。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"37f786f993","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)生育节制组。研究项目：生育节制的政策，家庭与婚姻等。","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"a105ecfaa8","type":"paragraph","text":"(4)人口统计组。研究人口统计理论与方法等。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"dc4eb67ee1","type":"paragraph","text":"(6)劳动问题组。因为人口与劳动问题密切联系，所以在该机构内又应适当开展劳动问题的科学研究，如劳动经济，劳动人民生活状况的调查，工人运动史等。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"f02e430bf6","type":"paragraph","text":"2．科学研究人员的配备。以上各组，每组平均约5人，共计25人，根据可能逐步配备。","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"e33e9245fe","type":"paragraph","text":"3．在北京附近选择30万左右人口的一个县作人口调查研究(附农村调查)的实验室。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"45659e97d8","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)选县人口调查研究计划。由陈达草拟。用本会名义向国务院科学规划委员会申请专款。","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"66f036b085","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)选县人口调查研究工作可与其它国家机关合作，但须征得合作机关的同意。如国家统计局，内务部，卫生部等。经费与人力由科学院与合作机关共同负担；估计每年约30万元，编制约30人左右。此项工作可逐步开展，由小到大，由少到多。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"61961c60ea","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)选县人口调查研究工作，可以解决以下目前急需的几个主要问题：人口普查的方法，为第二次全国人口普查提供建议；人事登记制度；生育节制；婚姻年龄的研究等。此外，还可附带进行农业与农民生活的调查研究。","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"b39e5bc0d3","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、城市社区调查研究，拟暂由人民大学社会调查研究室负责与科学院合作。开始在北京市进行调查研究工作。","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"90c432c0dc","type":"paragraph","text":"1．调查研究工作的具体领导由人大调查研究室负责，经费由人大负责，有需要时经费由科学院酌量补助；人员由本会酌量派研究员，研究助理参加工作。","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"9bcb65b738","type":"paragraph","text":"2．调查计划由人大调查研究室提出。推李景汉，吴景超，赵承信负责草拟。本会参与研究，由人大与科学院共同决定。","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"6c3a384c25","type":"paragraph","text":"丙、民族学研究。已有中央民族学院负责进行，建议添聘社会学专家参加世界民族志编写工作。","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"37cc0ff0d4","type":"paragraph","text":"1．经费及编制由民族学院负责；","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"27f6db349d","type":"paragraph","text":"2．拟请中宣部协助民族学院调集现在安排不当的原来社会学教授5—7人，经原机关同意，请高教部批准。","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"e609b7a408","type":"subtitle","text":"(三)关于筹备成立社会学系的计划。","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"fc7d9d0bf4","type":"paragraph","text":"1．为了培养人材，在高等学校成立社会学系，大家认为有必要，但需要一、二年准备。","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"6bbaf61e7b","type":"paragraph","text":"2．目前先拟教学计划，经大家讨论由本会提请中宣部、高教部考虑并作决定。教学计划推吴文藻、潘光旦、雷洁琼、林耀华等负责草拟。","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"8ca5a8f53f","type":"paragraph","text":"3．着手准备课程，希望二年内拿出一套比较成熟的教材。教材事先写好，大家讨论。","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"59e2d38c3d","type":"paragraph","text":"4．准备课程要有个地方，必须先集中一些人，北京可集中一些，上海等地也可集中一些。先搞调查研究，二年后可掌握大批实际材料，准备课程和开课都有基础。","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"f763a7e1c1","type":"paragraph","text":"5．条件成熟，可在北京，上海等地逐步建立社会学系。","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"0054b914ec","type":"subtitle","text":"(四)关于筹备成立中国社会学会","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"1787a21057","type":"paragraph","text":"1．先调查研究，了解情况，加以登记。会员包括过去教社会学的和社会学系毕业生。","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"efe3d6d142","type":"paragraph","text":"2．筹备工作由本会负责。与上海等地取得联系。","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"861c7ba386","type":"paragraph","text":"3．总会设在北京，其它各地可设分会。","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"479829c4b4","type":"paragraph","text":"4．个人发言记录：","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"13154850dd","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)吴景超发言：","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"fbf43df9dd","type":"paragraph","text":"一、成立社会学会。","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"b3f3ebc6c3","type":"paragraph","text":"二、在北京、上海、广州、成都四地成立社会系，可以很好的安排过去的人。","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"096dafa05e","type":"paragraph","text":"三、科学院成立社会调查研究所，先从人口下手。","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"590e331995","type":"paragraph","text":"四、人大有条件，如理论课、社会调查、人口与劳动、家庭、都市、社会工作等。有一、二年准备即可。","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"4e886f1e2e","type":"paragraph","text":"学生出路：市政府、法院、妇联、内务部、劳动部、工会。","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"b94db3856f","type":"appellation","text":"(2)费孝通发言：","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"da55981eba","type":"paragraph","text":"一、调查过去搞社会学工作的，准备成立学会。对过去搞过社会学工作的——教过书的，毕业生，进行安排。","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"8e45a14a91","type":"paragraph","text":"二、考虑一个比较长远的计划。","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"58e5de044d","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)培养后备。有步骤的来做，但须有个地方来准备。教学计划的目的，成立完整的系，先从开课始，从现在的基础来发展。多少时间，看条件(在个别的学校开，人大、北大、民族学院)。拟调柯象峰、应成一等五、六人到民族学院。","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"2295ed9f9d","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)先集中一批人，准备功课再分散，人大可集中一批，民族学院也可以。","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"a814ac2487","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)调查研究先开始，年轻人先搞调查研究，以北京为中心，作专题调查，二年以后就有资料，开课也有基础。","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"2ab219e7a8","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)吴文藻发言：","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"acfdac5115","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)安排人事，还有人尚未得到适当安排者，尽其安排。","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"d14e2acb0c","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)准备成立学会，全国性的总会在北京，但上海另应有个中心，因人多。北京也应成立学会。","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"23e543948b","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)建议在北大成立社会学系，将来放在那里再看。","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"e887dccb01","type":"paragraph","text":"30—40人先作实际工作。","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"b8cc8de4ff","type":"appellation","text":"(4)李景汉发言：","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"edc2248e59","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)成立社会学系，至少要有一、二年的准备，越稳越好。","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"be9c1b0f53","type":"subtitle","text":"(2)目前根据各方面能做的先做，找个实验县从事人口研究，一、二年内即可有资料。","index":74,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"72951089a4","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)社会学社会系设在综合大学好。","index":75,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"2d88a1b1dd","type":"paragraph","text":"改行者很多，从各方面来使其配个。","index":76,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"587fd85a18","type":"paragraph","text":"自觉自愿，一定能力。","index":77,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"0af2406ca0","type":"paragraph","text":"有条件，基本课有准备；拿出来学生没有话说。有吴(景超)的资本就行。","index":78,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"5cf9372979","type":"paragraph","text":"北京有个系更好，精力有限。","index":79,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"1f29c17cd0","type":"paragraph","text":"新作风，一心一德，大民主，大家商量，取得一致。","index":80,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"98c635e876","type":"appellation","text":"(6)雷洁琼发言：","index":81,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"4884fa078a","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)不是恢复社会学，而是创造新的社会学系。同意安排人也很重要。少数人准备教学计划到底有什么，八年经验，每人看社会学不一致，把社会学范围、培养人材搞清楚，拟几门功课，再加以安排。","index":82,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"c007e27c64","type":"paragraph","text":"民政、民族、理论调查，社会工作其范围应包括什么，先了解过去训练，现在搞什么。过去社会学很乱。人事安排不能完全自愿。第一步了解情况，第二步是教学课程、教学计划。人事都要安排很难。","index":83,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"930934d47c","type":"paragraph","text":"理论课四门，24—26，22门功课开什么。","index":84,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"a16acbf391","type":"appellation","text":"费孝通发言：","index":85,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"0f73ca9694","type":"paragraph","text":"人事问题：","index":86,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"e010b0f46a","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)没有失业的不动；","index":87,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"d700109a08","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)请其来开会可以抓一批人来。","index":88,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"21f1268bcf","type":"paragraph","text":"社会学基础：","index":89,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b412461c90"},{"id":"ccc7717b5f","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)暂时不能成立专门机构。1．